{"tid":2494471,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔就係所謂嘅樂壇判官","createTime":"2021-04-18T15:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T15:19:22.000Z","uid":64155,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6498898a78139d2a4a51b9e05a12bd242e14cc97","tid":2494471,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"香港人嘅性格就係諸多批評 唔識得欣賞<br />\n其實多啲欣賞少啲批評真係咁難咩<br />\n<br />\n首先我覺得家謙BB完全冇問題 呢啲就係佢嘅個人特色<br />\n就係咁大家先咁鍾意佢 <br />\n<br />\n泳兒 隔咗咁耐先再攞正式嘅獎(唔係CCTVB啲豬肉獎)今次仲要係全民投票 一人一票選出來 佢喊好正常 你哋又屌人假又剩<br />\n我睇見都戥佢感動喊埋一份<br />\n<br />\n之前欣宜肥你班仆街又話難頂 宜家人哋瘦咗少少又屌人呢樣果樣 你想點啫<br />\n<br />\n係咪想搞到香港artist個個抑鬱先肯收手"},{"pid":"1775a5d6535eb1290bc93a714dc6772476094791","tid":2494471,"uid":18230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"基本上全部同意，但<br />\n欣宜呢排邊有瘦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae18988444e75efc6f887409697917ebaf59855","tid":2494471,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前欣宜肥你班仆街又話難頂 宜家人哋瘦咗少少又屌人呢樣果樣</blockquote><br />\n想問佢邊忽有瘦到?"},{"pid":"90e725bcabb8ca8e66f6d001dcc33e0af31789ed","tid":2494471,"uid":322846,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU76xar3PTPEB9q3EUncRS1PSmvNuRsANxRqYPEE8o2Ge?filename=ynnLTyh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynnLTyh.jpg&h=1752f2bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大灣區代表偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪吹捧佢啦<br />\n喊還喊 死返去cctvb喊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514e102068a1cee541dd4bcae173eb07f4177a90","tid":2494471,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"泳兒咁多年終於有嘢拎下都唔俾人喊"},{"pid":"1fee62fc914e27d620ed9b4d0ccdf5f2f8d3d260","tid":2494471,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":